@startuml fig2_3_sequence_kyc
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "Conducteur" as Driver
participant "App Mobile" as Mobile #BBDEFB
participant "Express :8080" as Express #C8E6C9
participant "Verif MW" as VerifMW #A5D6A7
participant "FastAPI :8001" as FastAPI #FFF176
participant "Multer /uploads/" as Multer #CE93D8
database "PostgreSQL" as PG #CE93D8

== Phase 1 : Upload CNI ==
Driver -> Mobile : Telecharge CNI recto/verso
Mobile -> Mobile : MLKit OCR - extraction CIN
Mobile -> Express : POST /api/verification/upload-id
Express -> VerifMW : Verifier JWT + role driver
VerifMW --> Express : Autorise
Express -> Multer : Sauvegarde /uploads/verifications/
Multer --> Express : URLs securisees (auth-protected)
Express -> PG : Sauvegarde URLs verifications

== Phase 2 : Liveness + Verification ==
Driver -> Mobile : Capture selfie liveness (video)
Mobile -> Express : POST /api/verification/face
Express -> FastAPI : POST /verify-full\n{cin_recto, liveness_video, role=driver}\n[Header: X-Internal-Secret]

note over FastAPI #FFF9C4
  Pipeline InsightFace buffalo_l :
  1. FaceAnalyzer.extract_embedding(CIN)
  2. average_embedding_from_video(video)
  3. cosine similarity -> face_score
  4. LivenessDetector.check_video()
  5. AntiSpoofDetector.analyze()
  score = face x0.55 + live x0.25 + spoof x0.20
  Seuils conducteur:
  face >= 0.65 / liveness >= 0.65 / antispoof >= 0.60
end note

FastAPI --> Express : {score_global:0.94, verified:true}
Express -> PG : UPDATE users SET identity_status='verified'
Express --> Mobile : KYC approuve
@enduml